description:
Study 4 - Its Authority and Mission featuring Don Carson.

In #9 The Church, Study 4- Its Authority and Mission, the speaker is Don Carson.  Don is professor of New Testament at Trinity Evangelical Divinity School in Illinois.

Part 9: The Church includes six programs 1. Its Characteristics - Michele Guinness, 2. Its Main Description - Anne Graham Lotz, 3. Its Relationship to Christ - Michele Guinness, 4. Its Authority and Mission - Don Carson, 5. Its Ordinances - Tom Parsons, 6. Its Ministry and Order - Don Carson

"Scripture quotations taken from NIV version unless otherwise noted. Tape 9: The Church
Its Characteristics - Michele Guinness
Its Main Description - Anne Graham Lotz
Its Relationship to Christ - Michele Guinness
Its Authority and Mission - Don Carson
Its Ordinances - Tom Parsons
Its Ministry and Order - Don Carson Michele Guinness is from the famous Guinness beer family.  A Jewess, converted to Christianity, she is now a well-known author and broadcaster. Anne Graham Lotz is the daughter of evangelist Billy Graham and a well-known writer and speaker. Don Carson is professor of New Testament at Trinity Evangelical Divinity School in Illinois. Tom Parsons is a full-time student youth worker."

Director: Crawford Telfer
Starring: Don Carson
